lead_paragraph: Qatar has appointed a new coach to head its national soccer team in a bid to revive fading hopes of qualifying for its first World Cup finals in Russia in 2018.

headline.print_headline: Qatar Appoints New Coach in Bid to Revive 2018 World Cup Hopes
